	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I think the reason for the separate sweep result is that if the sweep unit calculates a result too large, it silences the channel even if sweep is disabled. This is why a lot of games don't use the pulse channels' bottom octave, as writing $00 causes anything in the bottom octave to instantly silence the channel.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


